@startuml
title RWA Tokenized Compliance System - Compliance Rule And Transfer Boundary

actor Investor
participant "Investor Dashboard" as InvestorUI
participant "Compliance API" as API
participant "Compliance Rule Service" as Rules
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Permissioned Token" as Token
participant "Identity Registry" as Registry

Investor -> InvestorUI : Subscribe or redeem
InvestorUI -> API : Lifecycle request
API -> Rules : Evaluate status, profile,\njurisdiction, lockup, cap
Rules -> DB : Read profiles and asset rules
Rules --> API : Allow or deny with reason

Investor -> Token : transfer(to, amount)
Token -> Registry : Check sender identity
Token -> Registry : Check receiver identity
Registry --> Token : Valid or rejected
Token --> Investor : Transfer succeeds or reverts
@enduml